channel.title: Dude what happened to my account?
channel.description: Hey guys I was playing one of the severs fishing when it logged me out, so I tried to get back on it said "account had been disabled" so I went to another sever...didn't let me on, another...didn't let me on, restarted my computer tried a world...didn't let me on. So what happened, I can't play moparscape anymore? what did I do? :confused: I was fishing, not saying or doing anything else, then bam off I go, doesn't really sound far, someone help?
